mikespub/rvolz-bicbucstriim.name: mikespub/rvolz-bicbucstriim
mikespub/rvolz-bicbucstriim.description: BicBucStriim streams books, digital books. It fills a gap in the functionality of current NAS devices that provide access to music, videos and photos -- but not books. BicBucStriim fills this gap and provides web-based access to your e-book collection.
